    "description": "Are you a skilled Consultant Physician looking for your next big career move? PGIMER Advisory Limited in Aurangabad offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout PGIMER Advisory Limited:\nPGIMER Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure patient privacy and maintain confidentiality\n• Administer medications and treatments as prescribed\n• Attend continuing medical education programs and training\n• Conduct routine health assessments and screenings\n• Adhere to NABH/JCI accreditation standards\n• Coordinate with multidisciplinary teams for comprehensive patient management\n• Diagnose and treat medical conditions following established protocols\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Diploma or Degree in Hospitality Management\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Medical Coding\n• Proficiency in Infection Control\n• Proficiency in Diagnostic Skills\n• Proficiency in Pharmacovigilance\n• Proficiency in Patient Care\n• Proficiency in ICD-10\n• Proficiency in Health Informatics\n• Proficiency in ICU Management\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Referral bonus program\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Flexible working hours\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Aurangabad, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with PGIMER Advisory Limited!",
